This project helps you measure the size of the bed. Also, helps you find the appropiate mattress, and rug for the bed. 
All is done through the use of functions with pointer arguments that will later be used in the main function. 

First, thing it asks is for the measurements of the Bedroom.
Second, it asks you for the shape of the rug tht you have.
  Depending on the users decision the program decides to use one function or the other.
Third, enter the measurements of the rug and the system will tell you if the rug fits.
